## v1.0.0 → v1.1.0 (2026-06-13)
**Changed by:** Session — issue #1189 python-version-consistency DRY refactor
**Verification:** verified-local
### What changed
- Added RUF022 (`__all__` not sorted) and I001 (import block un-sorted) patterns
- Added `ruff check --fix` as preferred resolution path for `[*]`-fixable rules
### Why
Manual reordering of `__all__` and import blocks with `as` aliases fails because ruff/isort uses the aliased name for ordering, not the original symbol name. Three errors were fixed in one pass across two files using `pixi run ruff check --fix`.
